{"type":null,"faqId":8794,"title":"荣耀3X（G750-T00）怎样后台播放与退出音乐，歌词同步","answer":"1.后台播放：进入音乐播放器，播放任意音频文件，播放过程中按Home键。<br />\n2.退出音乐：在音乐播放界面，点击手机Menu键，选择退出，在弹出的框上选择确定，即可退出音乐应用。<br />\n3.歌词同步：当歌曲和对应的歌词存储在手机同一目录时，用户播放这首歌曲，歌词会自动加载。在播放界面，按住屏幕向左拖动，可以拖动到歌词界面。","faqTypeId":1086,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"9377","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Camera-Gallery","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1396080667000,"seriesProductName":"G750-T00","visitedTimes":76,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"音乐","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}